{
  "stem": "10549.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans used to come, come to the labor office, and they used to request so many Jewish workers for their purpose, whatever purpose it was, to clean the facility, to wash or to carry coal or to carry furniture or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one time I was picked up by [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the German Gestapo headquarters, whoever it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we worked on the Gestapo headquarters as a laborer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was carrying coal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was carrying furniture because the Gestapo were in charge of liquidating and confiscating all the wealth or whatever they were taking away from everybody, and mostly Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I become one of the workers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because I became a useful person-- when the ghetto started in Cracow, they designated one building for their workers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that headquarters, there was a lot of other profession, like-- not profession, I mean, carpenters, mechanics, car mechanics, and shoemakers, tailors, and so, so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there was over 140 people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who were servicing that headquarters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that-- after that, I met somebody over there who was from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And instead of being a block laborer, he took me to help him to be a painter, to paint.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I become a painter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I learn how to paint, and I become a painter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I had a little-- it was not so hard for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was much, much easier work by being a painter than carrying coal from the cellar to the fourth or fifth floor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
